channel.title: CNN News: Teen rescued after 100 hours of Quake
channel.description:
Just saw this on my RSS, now, how many of you thought this was about quake the game and never stopped to think that it could be a teen trapped in rubble after an earthquake?
Personally I though it was just some addicted kid to Quake the game lol...
...I even had a joke for it!!!
Teen almost had a Heart Strogg lol

sersoft:

It’s impossible to survive 100 hours of quake gameplay. BTW, you forgot to post the link so I googled it, and the dailymotion title is even funnier.

Quake: ALL UR HOURS ARE BELONG TO US

Definately waiting for someone to say “challenge accepted”

Maybe playing Quake 1, 2 and 4 in one session, and whatever time is left on quake 3 or live? :S
